{"tid":1941170,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"對服務部部員好失望","createTime":"2020-03-24T08:56:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T10:18:01.000Z","uid":105678,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e0da7c572dbe6910782b4fdae5fc605e74dcc83b","tid":1941170,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T08:56:26.000Z","msg":"成日淨係識盲反我地鋼鍊能，自己毒撚睇開廢萌番打J就覺得所有動物台都係咁<br />\n<br />\n睇刀劍神域就幻想自己係銅人，一秒十六刀，現實中自己一秒射16次昨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鏡煉就唔同，有哲學又夠藝術，一句等價交換啟蒙幾多小朋友，由我地睇鋼煉嘅00後香港人入哂三大神科就明套嘢幾神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n反觀服務部最高學歴嘅木之那櫻都加入共青團做愛國人士，就知睇刀劍害咗幾多毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結論：睇鋼煉=高等精英，其他動物都係垃圾"},{"pid":"679baa80babef828d500cafc91fd017e89efee43","tid":1941170,"uid":307737,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T09:08:24.000Z","msg":"判定會員<span style=\"color: red;\">委員長(暖暖部）</span>為引發紛爭嘅元凶，即將展開武力介入<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YuGHKSj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYuGHKSj.jpg&h=3fe6d4d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"69432dfea2f6020f41885ad726b939b5c8a99f72","tid":1941170,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"679baa80babef828d500cafc91fd017e89efee43","tid":1941170,"uid":307737,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T09:08:24.000Z","msg":"判定會員<span style=\"color: red;\">委員長(暖暖部）</span>為引發紛爭嘅元凶，即將展開武力介入<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YuGHKSj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYuGHKSj.jpg&h=3fe6d4d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T09:11:14.000Z","msg":"我老死迫爆神條女用渣古都可以射柒你啲辣殺高達<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99bfcf7c686fe318a65b88612e9c6291ccd934bf","tid":1941170,"uid":310914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T09:13:24.000Z","